  adalogger
  Creates WiFi hotspot and serves CAN message logs via a not so minimal hotspot
  Transmits heartbeat so it appears as a visible device on the FRC CAN bus
  
  Pins:
    RED_PIN   = 15 (LEDC PWM)
    GREEN_PIN = 13 (LEDC PWM)
    BLUE_PIN  = 14 (LEDC PWM)
    CAN TX    = GPIO 4
    CAN RX    = GPIO 5
  
  Status LED Indicators:
   - Booting: Solid red
   - WiFi AP Ready: Solid green
   - System Ready / Idle: Solid blue
   - FRC CAN Heartbeat Detected: Brief magenta flash (returns to blue)
   - CAN Bus Error (bus-off): No visual indication (error counted internally)
 
